/************************************************************
 * HiBob ↔ Gusto Comparison Generator (Yes/No version)
 *
 * Recreated & fixed: single-file Google Apps Script.
 *
 * Key fixes and improvements:
 *  - Sheet-aware header mapping to avoid cross-sheet alias collisions.
 *  - Robust fallback lookups for Bob FLSA and Gusto employee type so Type_Bob
 *    comes from Bob's FLSA and Type_Gusto is populated from Gusto.
 *  - Safer date comparisons (use Date objects).
 *  - More tolerant comp-rate parser (additional 'per' variants and explicit ISO codes).
 *  - Canonical type constants to avoid accidental mismatches by case/whitespace.
 *  - Small readability & defensive checks.
 ************************************************************/

